textbook parser:

@author{abc}{abc@@def.org}   is parsed into   
        <prop nm='attributes'>
          <text>
            <prop nm='#attr-name'>name</prop>
            <prop nm='data'>abc</prop>
          </text>
          <text>
            <prop nm='#attr-name'>email</prop>
            <prop nm='data'>abc</prop>
          </text>
          <text>
            <prop nm='#attr-name'>email</prop>
            <prop nm='data'>@def.org</prop>
          </text>
        </prop>
